reviewText: This dvd is from the Pump tour in Philly and not the Permanent Vacation tour as the title might lead one to think. It is pro shot with multiple camera's and the sound is from the board. Those are the positives. Here are the negatives. The sound isn't great and neither is the video quality. None of this has been remastered and my experience with bootlegs tells me that this is not an official Aerosmith release. It is very much like a bootleg although it is a silverback dvd and not a dvd-r. The bands performance is very average here for them which is still better than most.
Title: N/A
